---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="about - being bored"
  description="about being bored - a web app to reset your mind through intentional boredom"
>
  <Header />

  <div id="hero" class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 pt-20">
    <a
      href="/"
      class="text-stone-500 text-sm hover:text-stone-400 transition-colors underline"
      >back</a
    >

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-100 mt-4 mb-8">about</h1>

    <p class="text-stone-400 mb-4">
      created this because, i dont want to work, but i need to work. i find
      myself literally doing anything but work. ironically, i created this while
      procrastinating from work.
    </p>

    <p class="text-stone-400 mb-4">
      i realized it was because literally anything is more interesting than
      work. then i thought about
      <a
        href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tsYKn0gMN6A"
        class="text-blue-500 underline hover:text-blue-400 active:text-blue-600 transition-colors"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        this video by bigboxSWE
      </a>, where the solution is to win by being bored. he calls it the
      "boredom principle", and literally stares at his code editor for 10min
      doing absolutely nothing, then he finds the motivation to do work because
      literally anything is more interesting and fun than looking at a blank
      code editor
    </p>

    <p class="text-stone-400 mb-4">
      so here it is, a web app to literally make you bored, to ironically make
      you motivated to do whatever it is that you are putting off. hope it helps
    </p>

    <p class="text-stone-400">
      by <a
        href="https://gjtiquia.com"
        class="hover:text-stone-300 transition-colors underline"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">gjtiquia</a
      >
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
